  <summary date="2021-08-04T02:43:53Z" status="Introduced in House">NEPA Accountability and Enforcement Act

This bills establishes (1) deadlines for federal agencies to complete reviews of the environmental effects of proposed major federal actions, and (2) penalties for agencies that do not comply with these deadlines.</summary>
